reviewText: A dance company that keeps alive the dances of the every-day folks in Eastern Europe and the Russia of Asia.  Well done!

Lost my copy.  Had to get a new one.  Whole thing is spectacular, but the Partisans and Night on Bald Mountain will never be matched by anything any ballet company, nor any cirque du soleil show could ever dream up.  These two works are the genius of an artist from a time gone by and should be viewed by all dancers, dance professors, and aspiring choreographers of any dance genre.  Watch and learn!
